reviewText: I saw it when it first came out, and think there is some footage missing from this, and think there may have been an alternate ending.  But I could be wrong, it has been a couple decades..

This dvd is junk.the first dvd that I got keeps on freezing so I return it in exchange for the same title..When I got the replacement dvd same story it freezes and won't forward even if I push the forward arrow. I'm glad I was reimbursed.
